column5: Up at 0420, bowl of oatmeal and coffee, off to the spot, wait a few minutes for it to get a little closer to dawn.  Set up, miss the first one.  Second roebag did the trick. Weighed in at 6 lb 11 oz.  Missed a couple more but this started the day off right.
Next week watch your rear view. LOL  Nice fish buddy.  BTW My back and rear do like that heat. High is a killer for too long. LOL
Ya, no falling asleep on high with that seat heater.
fisherman, great clean chromer, if i was going 2 eat a trout, that is the size for me.
